column5: Just word from Leslie at Lakair, I've been accepted for temporary residence. Will be there 21,22 23rd June.  Finally I will be able to put some faces to some names.  Looking forward to it
Be great to finally meet you Jack! We'll be there all week.  Wayne and Leah
Great news Nanook.  Look forward to meeting you.  Joey
Super. I'm sure the trip will be enjoyable for you.  Don't forget the camera.
You won't regret it jack, it'll be good to see you there.  Maureen
And I'm riding "shotgun/navigator" for Jack...  However I'll be staying in Maureen's cabin as I suffer badly from claustrophobia...even when icefishing in a hut I need the seat by the door...
